text: José Carlos Borunda Zaragoza (born 22 February 1971) is a Mexican politician from the National Action Party. From 2000 to 2003 he served as Deputy of the LVIII Legislature of the Mexican Congress representing Chihuahua. ==References== Category:1971 births Category:Living people Category:Politicians from Chihuahua (state) Category:Members of the Chamber of Deputies (Mexico) Category:National Action Party (Mexico) politicians Category:21st-century Mexican politicians Category:John F.
